{"tid":56944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先喺屋企行樓梯見到隻貓","createTime":"2016-12-27T15:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T15:49:35.000Z","uid":20263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a753d712fe59f7daf3313606ac919f685190900","tid":56944,"uid":20263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/231337_2e60b53e94f27364c05b1ca7a1e57d0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F231337_2e60b53e94f27364c05b1ca7a1e57d0b.jpg&h=28be0350&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma8UfzWwyKZtFnJBY13P11e4sC5ZcJcqz2mPg3RWS6ZmX?filename=i12yTBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi12yTBY.jpg&h=da55d1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行過見到隻貓仔捲埋自己喺角落<br />\n我呢邊好應風好凍<br />\n我都凍到震<br />\n即刻大愛撚上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得好可憐<br />\n<br />\n乜都做唔到，又唔可以帶佢返屋企<br />\n後尾即刻返去拎條毛巾俾佢cum<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/233708_be62c18208d51bc5a8fcb0af463e344d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F233708_be62c18208d51bc5a8fcb0af463e344d.jpg&h=593de443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上到去仲喺度<br />\n<br />\n一接近佢，即刻就跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知佢跑去邊<br />\n<br />\n唯有放係嗰個位希望佢陣間返去暖少少啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/233942_7e31bc493ed800c5ddbd7aa0d75192fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F233942_7e31bc493ed800c5ddbd7aa0d75192fd.jpg&h=3aed540a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b073191ee3a4ef8dc91f6d06d8d5a75f2e9c5206","tid":56944,"uid":8074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:41:31.000Z","msg":"比個紙箱佢嘛"},{"pid":"3ae11a6b7750fdf3b97aea0d1086b257c9cca458","tid":56944,"uid":26471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"似有人養？"},{"pid":"a6dfc5c322763b76fd48b9fcc1647688e1f2c96a","tid":56944,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"住咁高都有貓。。走失！？"},{"pid":"8d6b938accb50d9b98ca628295329ab04cf501f4","tid":56944,"uid":30227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"好得意但好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望佢搵到位避風"},{"pid":"9a6b73ee0461df28ee240aad1b4f8bffee6ab9bf","tid":56944,"uid":20263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"如果係走失貓，希望主人快啲發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7a30b925fc6753accc75a1bc702cb39fda1913","tid":56944,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"咁凍仲係出面唔似有人養喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有可能係走失/啱啱流放<br />\n我日日會路過某個街市<br />\n個街市出面有隻流浪貓<br />\n但係暖嘅日子先見到佢<br />\n凍個陣佢都會自己&quot;lei&quot;埋"}]}